            img._pixel-12.js-dotted(src="images/four-section/pexel-12.svg", alt="")
            img._pixel-13.js-dotted(src="images/four-section/pexel-13.svg", alt="")
        ._info.-s2
          ._text.js-four-text-2
            p The peaceful coexistence was shattered. Angels and Demons, once allies in the stewardship of Etena, diverged on their philosophies of Etena Dustâ€™s use.
