    img._cloud-2.js-four-cloud-2(src="images/four-section/cloud-2.png", alt="") 
    ._container.-s3
      ._row.js-four-contain-3
        ._info.-s3
          ._subtitle.js-four-subtitle
            p In the shadows of a world recovering from its own greed and violence, the Demons sensed a stirring, the faint whispers of Etena Dust rekindling.
            p Amidst this resurgence, three clans of Demons emerged, ready to claim their stake in the rebirth of their world.

    ._container.-s4.js-four-contain-4
