          ._planet-img.-i2
            img(src="images/four-section/planet-2.png", alt="")
          ._planet-wrap
            ._planet-title.title-h1 The Voidwalkers
            ._planet-text Weavers of cosmic energies, embody the vastness and mystery of the universe. They navigate the space between stars, harnessing the celestial power to bend the fabric of reality itself.

        ._planet.js-four-planet-3
          ._planet-img.-i3
            img(src="images/four-section/planet-3.png", alt="")
          ._planet-wrap
            ._planet-title.title-h1 The Tideseekers
            ._planet-text guardians of water, embody the depth and adaptability of the ocean. Their spirits flow with the grace and relentless force of the tides, a clan as nurturing as it is formidable.
